  <brief_title>Validation of CardioQ Versus PiCCO in Children</brief_title>
  <acronym>CQPiCCO</acronym>
  <official_title>Validation of an Ultrasound Oesophageal Doppler Cardiac Output Monitor (ODM+, CardioQ) Versus a Transpulmonary Thermodilution Cardiac Output Monitor (TPTD, PiCCO)</official_title>
